snippet.title: Mistery - Official Gameplay Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the gameplay showcase trailer for Mistery, a multiplayer survival social deduction game developed by Game Frontier. Collect materials, survive the dangers, and complete tasks as other players wield the ability to transform into supernatural monsters for the attack. Mistery is launching on PC (Steam) at a later date.

#Mistery #Gameplay #SocialDeduction
